    CrabsTutorial

    Christina Barrilleaux

    2023-11-14

    CrabsTutorial.Rmd

    This package is used to process crabs data. This data is from a crabbing contest and includes various physical charateristics and location information. It includes functions to plot data, statistical analysis, and more.

    Required Packages
